    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":3867,"title":"Tuck And Spin","topic":"Community","slug":"tuck-and-spin","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/df8eaaf759dddac8c650b072dc10fd16/54c52e1603a60cbdf87c024410176a5b.jpg"},"photoCredit":"The City of Bentonville","date":"2021-11-17","content":"<p>Get your Ice Skates ready, because the ice skating rink in Bentonville opens this Saturday, <a href=\"http://bentonvillear.com/887/The-Rink-at-Lawrence-Plaza?fbclid=IwAR30MQlRybd_8q-4-9T2sBoE6UmY8t19-hHT87YD00n6s-sBqSx5IA-ZQPg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nov. 20</a>.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Place:</strong> It’s called The Rink and it’s at <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Lawrence+Plaza/@36.3747919,-94.2100085,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x87c91a974976fff7:0xd9499d33b4435838!8m2!3d36.3747919!4d-94.2078198\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Lawrence Plaza 214 NE A St</a>. The Rink is 7,000 sq/ft of ice&nbsp;over a concrete pad in downtown and <a href=\"http://bentonvillear.com/DocumentCenter/View/8238/2021-2022-Rink-Schedule\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">stays chilled and solid</a> through the first two weeks of February 2022.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Price: </strong>Tickets to ice skate are <a href=\"http://bentonvillear.com/887/The-Rink-at-Lawrence-Plaza?fbclid=IwAR30MQlRybd_8q-4-9T2sBoE6UmY8t19-hHT87YD00n6s-sBqSx5IA-ZQPg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">$7</a> per person per session. Or you can get a Family Season Pass Ice Rink Membership for <a href=\"https://apm.activecommunities.com/playbentonville/Membership?package_id=265\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">$75</a>, and it is good for 6 family members per day. There is opportunity to host <a href=\"http://bentonvillear.com/1093/Private-Parties\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">private parties</a> on the rink as well as take <a href=\"http://bentonvillear.com/1375/Ice-Skating-Lessons\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">lessons</a>.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Click <a href=\"http://bentonvillear.com/887/The-Rink-at-Lawrence-Plaza?fbclid=IwAR30MQlRybd_8q-4-9T2sBoE6UmY8t19-hHT87YD00n6s-sBqSx5IA-ZQPg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a> for more information.&nbsp;</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"tuck-and-spin"}},
